>Daniel_Piechnick: ABETUY H7 BEAUTY +30 30
#note what the...I look at the pairings and I have my second repeat pairing in a row. This is the point in the tournament where they finally went full KOTH. There would be many more repeat pairings to come. We were all the way at table 4 because based on the round 14 standings he was in 7th and I was in 8th. Because the standings were a round behind I wasn't really aware that I was actuall in 6th place at this point.
>jd: AGKORRX G7 ARK +31 31
