#note This was a really big game. In retrospect, though I wasn't likely to win if I found TENTORIUM, it's the kind of play that I am capable of finding at times.It's easy to second-guess yourself but I think I was already starting to feel a lot of fatigue. This is something worth worrying about in the long run if I want to be a contender at worlds. I've been in long tournaments before (reno and such) but this might be the toughest tournament in the world, and I definitely felt my energy levels getting low in the afternoons of days 2 and 4. I need to figure out ways to keep playing at a high level even late into afternoons. Food for thought.  I would go on to play some of my worst games of the tournament during the afternoon. 
